<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Top-up Confirmed</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">Top-up Confirmed!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
    <p>Hi {{user.name}},</p>
    
    <p>Your top-up has been successfully added to your eSIM profile.</p>
    
    <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6;">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #8b5cf6;">Top-up Details</h2>
      <p><strong>ICCID:</strong> {{profile.iccid}}</p>
      <p><strong>Plan:</strong> {{plan.name}}</p>
      <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{topup.currency}} {{topup.amount}}</p>
      <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{topup.status}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Your additional data should be available shortly. Check your eSIM status in <a href="{{appUrl}}/my-esims" style="color: #1e90ff;">My eSIMs</a>.</p>
    
    <p>Safe travels!<br>The Voyage Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
    <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

